headline: DaVita (NYSE:DVA) Beats Q1 Sales Targets
summary: Dialysis provider DaVita Inc. (NYSE:DVA) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q1 CY2025, with sales up 5% year on year to $3.22 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2 per share was 1% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
